NAME
    uSAC::HTTP - Duct Tape x Chainsaw

SYNOPSIS
      #For servers
      use uSAC::HTTP::Server;

      #For clients
      use uSAC:HTTP::Client;

DESCRIPTION
    This is grouping of core uSAC::HTTP data structures and modules to write
    HTTP like client and server alpplications.

    Normally you would import the server or client (or both) to add it to
    your application.

    This is very much unfinished and under heavy development and changes....

